PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of DARLENE MANDEVILLE, of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Cecile McCauley, whose term has expired.
